h they are different indicators the data to track both 15.a.1 and 15.b.1 is currently the same.\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"parseErrors\":[]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":[{\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Target:\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"spanType\":\"span-bold\"},{\"text\":\" &acirc;&#128;&#156;Mobilize significant resources from all sources and at all levels to finance sustainable forest management and provide adequate incentives to developing countries to advance such management, including for conservation and reforestation.&acirc;&#128;&#157;\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"parseErrors\":[]}],\"type\":\"sticky-right\",\"right\":[{\"type\":\"chart-story\",\"items\":[{\"chart\":{\"url\":\"https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/total-oda-for-biodiversity-by-recipient\",\"type\":\"chart\",\"parseErrors\":[]},\"narrative\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":[{\"text\":\"ODA for biodiversity by recipient\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"parseErrors\":[]},\"technical\":[]},{\"chart\":{\"url\":\"https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/total-oda-for-biodiversity-by-donor\",\"type\":\"chart\",\"parseErrors\":[]},\"narrative\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":[{\"text\":\"ODA for biodiversity by donor\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"parseErrors\":[]},\"technical\":[]}],\"parseErrors\":[]}],\"parseErrors\":[]},{\"text\":[{\"text\":\"Combat global poaching and trafficking\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"type\":\"heading\",\"level\":2,\"supertitle\":[{\"text\":\"Target 15.c\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"parseErrors\":[]},{\"left\":[{\"text\":[{\"text\":\"Poaching and trafficking wildlife\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"type\":\"heading\",\"level\":3,\"supertitle\":[{\"text\":\"SDG Indicator 15.c.1\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"parseErrors\":[]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"value\":[{\"children\":[{\"text\":\"Definition of the SDG indicator:\",\"spanType\":\"span-simple-text\"}],\"spanType\":\"span-bold\"},{\"text\":\" Indica