urrentColor\" d=\"M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z\"></path></svg></span><span>Goal 15: Life on land</span></div></div><header class=\"centered-article-header align-center grid grid-cols-8 span-cols-8 col-start-4 grid-md-cols-6 span-md-cols-12 col-md-start-2\"><div class=\"centered-article-header__title-container col-start-2 span-cols-6 span-md-cols-6 col-md-start-1\"><h3 class=\"centered-article-header__supertitle span-cols-8\">Sustainable Development Goal 15</h3><h1 class=\"centered-article-header__title\">Sustainably manage forests, combat desertification, halt and reverse land degradation, halt biodiversity loss</h1></div><div class=\"centered-article-header__meta-container col-start-2 span-cols-6 span-md-cols-6 col-md-start-1 grid grid-cols-2 \"><div class=\"span-cols-1 span-sm-cols-2\"><div class=\"centered-article-header__byline\">By: <a href=\"/team/\">Our World in Data team</a></div><div class=\"centered-article-header__dateline body-3-medium-italic\">July 18, 2023</div></div><div class=\"centered-article-header__links span-cols-1 span-sm-cols-2\"><a href=\"#article-citation\" class=\"body-1-regular display-block\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"book\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-book \" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M96 0C43 0 0 43 0 96L0 416c0 53 43 96 96 96l288 0 32 0c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32l0-64c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32l0-320c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32L384 0 96 0zm0 384l256 0 0 64L96 448c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32s14.3-32 32-32zm32-240c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16l192 0c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16s-7.2 16-16 16l-192 0c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16zm16 48l192 0c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16s-7.2 16-16 16l-192 0c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16s7.2-16 16-16z\"></path></svg>Cite this article</a><a href=\"#article-licence\" class=\"body-3-medium display-block\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fab\" data-icon=\"creative-commons\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-creative-commons \" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 496 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M245.83 214.87l-33.22 17.28c-9.43-19.58-25.24-19.93-27.46-19.93-22.13 0-33.22 14.61-33.22 43.84 0 23.57 9.21 43.84 33.22 43.84 14.47 0 24.65-7.09 30.57-21.26l30.55 15.5c-6.17 11.51-25.69 38.98-65.1 38.98-22.6 0-73.96-10.32-73.96-77.05 0-58.69 43-77.06 72.63-77.06 30.72-.01 52.7 11.95 65.99 35.86zm143.05 0l-32.78 17.28c-9.5-19.77-25.72-19.93-27.9-19.93-22.14 0-33.22 14.61-33.22 43.84 0 23.55 9.23 43.84 33.22 43.84 14.45 0 24.65-7.09 30.54-21.26l31 15.5c-2.1 3.75-21.39 38.98-65.09 38.98-22.69 0-73.96-9.87-73.96-77.05 0-58.67 42.97-77.06 72.63-77.06 30.71-.01 52.58 11.95 65.56 35.86zM247.56 8.05C104.74 8.05 0 123.11 0 256.05c0 138.49 113.6 248 247.56 248 129.93 0 248.44-100.87 248.44-248 0-137.87-106.62-248-248.44-248zm.87 450.81c-112.54 0-203.7-93.04-203.7-202.81 0-105.42 85.43-203.27 203.72-203.27 112.53 0 202.82 89.46 202.82 203.26-.01 121.69-99.68 202.82-202.84 202.82z\"></path></svg>Reuse our work freely</a></div></div></header><p class=\"article-block__text col-start-5 span-cols-6 col-md-start-3 span-md-cols-10 span-sm-cols-12 col-sm-start-2\"><em><span>Sustainable Development Goal 15 is to &acirc;&#128;&#156;conserve life on land&acirc;&#128;&#157;, </span></em><em><a href=\"https://www.un.org/sustainabledevelopment/biodiversity/\" class=\"span-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span>according to the United Nations.</span></a></em></p><p class=\"article-block__text col-start-5 span-cols-6 col-md-start-3 span-md-cols-10 span-sm-cols-12 col-sm-start-2\"><span>The visualizations and data below present the global perspective on where the world stands today and how it has changed over time.</span></p><p class=\"article-block__text col-start-5 span-cols-6 col-md-start-3 span-md-cols-10 span-sm-cols-12 col-sm-start-2\"><span>The </span><a href=\"https://unstats.un.org/sdgs/indicators/Global%20Indicator%20Framework%20after%202023%20refinement_Eng.pdf\" class=\"span-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span>UN has defined</span></a><span> 12 </span><em><span>targets</span></em><span> and 14 </span><em><span>indicators</span></em><span> for SDG 15. Targets specify the goals and indicators represent the metrics by which the world aims to track whether these targets are achieved. Below we quote the original text of all targets and show the data on the agreed indicators.</span></p><nav class=\"article-block__toc grid grid-cols-8 col-start-4 span-cols-8 grid-md-cols-10 col-md-start-3 span-md-cols-10 grid-sm-cols-12 span-sm-cols-12 col-sm-start-2 toc\" role=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-controls=\"toc-menu\" data-track-note=\"toc_toggle\"><button aria-label=\"Toggle table of contents\" id=\"toc-menu-button\" class=\"toc-toggle span-cols-6 span-md-cols-8 span-sm-cols-10\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-controls=\"toc-menu\" data-track-note=\"toc_toggle\"><span>List of targets and indicators</span><span><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"plus\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-plus \" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 448 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M256 80c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32l0 144L48 224c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32l144 0 0 144c0 17.7 14.3 32 32 32s32-14.3 32-32l0-144 144 0c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32l-144 0 0-144z\"></path></svg></span></button><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"rah-static rah-static--height-zero toc-content span-cols-6 span-md-cols-8 span-sm-cols-10\" style=\"height:0;overflow:hidden\"><div style=\"transition:opacity 500ms ease 0ms;-webkit-transition:opacity 500ms ease 0ms;opacity:0\"><ul id=\"toc-menu\" role=\"menu\" aria-labelledby=\"toc-menu-button\"><li class=\"section\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#target-15-1-conserve-and-restore-terrestrial-and-freshwater-ecosystems\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">Target 15.1</span>Conserve and restore terrestrial and freshwater ecosystems</a><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"arrow-down\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-arrow-down \" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 384 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M169.4 470.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l160-160c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L224 370.8 224 64c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32l0 306.7L54.6 265.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l160 160z\"></path></svg></li><li class=\"subsection\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#sdg-indicator-15-1-1-forest-cover\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">SDG Indicator 15.1.1</span>Forest cover</a></li><li class=\"subsection\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#sdg-indicator-15-1-2-protection-of-important-biodiversity-areas\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">SDG Indicator 15.1.2</span>Protection of important biodiversity areas</a></li><li class=\"section\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#target-15-2-end-deforestation-and-restore-degraded-forests\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">Target 15.2</span>End deforestation and restore degraded forests</a><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"arrow-down\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-arrow-down \" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 384 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M169.4 470.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l160-160c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L224 370.8 224 64c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32l0 306.7L54.6 265.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l160 160z\"></path></svg></li><li class=\"subsection\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#sdg-indicator-15-2-1-sustainable-forest-management\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">SDG Indicator 15.2.1</span>Sustainable forest management</a></li><li class=\"section\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#target-15-3-end-desertification-and-restore-degraded-land\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">Target 15.3</span>End desertification and restore degraded land</a><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"arrow-down\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-arrow-down \" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 384 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M169.4 470.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l160-160c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L224 370.8 224 64c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32l0 306.7L54.6 265.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l160 160z\"></path></svg></li><li class=\"subsection\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#sdg-indicator-15-3-1-end-land-degradation\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">SDG Indicator 15.3.1</span>End land degradation</a></li><li class=\"section\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#target-15-4-ensure-conservation-of-mountain-ecosystems\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">Target 15.4</span>Ensure conservation of mountain ecosystems</a><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"arrow-down\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-arrow-down \" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 384 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M169.4 470.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l160-160c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L224 370.8 224 64c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32l0 306.7L54.6 265.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l160 160z\"></path></svg></li><li class=\"subsection\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#sdg-indicator-15-4-1-coverage-of-important-sites-for-mountain-biodiversity\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">SDG Indicator 15.4.1</span>Coverage of important sites for mountain biodiversity</a></li><li class=\"subsection\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#sdg-indicator-15-4-2-vegetation-coverage-of-mountainous-areas\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">SDG Indicator 15.4.2</span>Vegetation coverage of mountainous areas</a></li><li class=\"section\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#target-15-5-protect-biodiversity-and-natural-habitats\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">Target 15.5</span>Protect biodiversity and natural habitats</a><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"arrow-down\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-arrow-down \" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 384 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M169.4 470.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l160-160c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L224 370.8 224 64c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32l0 306.7L54.6 265.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l160 160z\"></path></svg></li><li class=\"subsection\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#sdg-indicator-15-5-1-species-extinction-risk\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">SDG Indicator 15.5.1</span>Species extinction risk</a></li><li class=\"section\" role=\"none\"><a href=\"#target-15-6-protect-access-to-genetic-resources-and-fair-sharing-of-the-benefits\" data-track-note=\"toc_link\" role=\"menuitem\"><span class=\"supertitle\">Target 15.6</span>Protect access to genetic resources and fair sharing of the benefits</a><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fas\" data-icon=\"arrow-down\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-arrow-down \" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 384 512\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M169.4 470.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l160-160c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L224 370.8 224 64c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32l0 306.7L54.6 265.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 3