(7, 'Accelerating climate change', 'sdg15', 'uploads/683726474e67d_aaa.png', '提供與永續發展目標 15 相關的進展和挑戰的數據驅動洞察，包括關鍵指標的視覺化和分析。', 'https://datatopics.worldbank.org/sdgatlas/goal-15-life-on-land/?lang=en', 2, '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html prefix=\"og: http://ogp.me/ns#\" lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"content-security-policy\" content=\"\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/_layout.c125686a.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/_layout.f7686f46.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/isScreenshotting.a5eff135.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/ReferenceCountrySelector.d89a7dca.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/triggerAnalytics.d86ce451.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/_page.d73b280b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/GlobeLegend.6759de0e.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/Lens.993ccd89.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/Minimap.5b98d65a.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/MultipleCell.af06df2d.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/MultiplesContainer.efde3abf.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/EmissionBars.60be6901.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/PovertyClimateScroller.a5a22934.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/TweenedLine.45369aa8.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/TweenedCircle.a7ef3e02.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/PovertyLineRegionBeeswarm.06f2ead5.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n		<link href=\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/assets/PovertyLineScroller.d3