odiversity, but levels vary by year and region.</h1>\n      <h2 class=\"svelte-cy315q\">Total official development assistance for biodiversity, by recipient countries (millions of constant 2020 United States dollars)</h2></div>\n  <div class=\"graphic svelte-cy315q\"><img src=\"https://datatopics.worldbank.org/sdgatlas/assets/supplementary/en/goal15/sdg15_oda.png\" class=\"svelte-cy315q\"></div>\n  \n  <hr class=\"svelte-cy315q\">\n  <p class=\"source svelte-cy315q\"><span class=\"source-text\">Source: <!-- HTML_TAG_START -->[link: https://unstats.un.org/sdgs/dataportal/ SDG Global Database]<!-- HTML_TAG_END --></span>\n    <span class=\"download svelte-cy315q\">DOWNLOAD\n      <span class=\"download-icon svelte-cy315q\"><svg class=\"svelte-fa  svelte-1cj2gr0\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-.125em;transform-origin:center;overflow:visible\" viewbox=\"0 0 512 512\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><g transform=\"translate(256 256)\" transform-origin=\"128 0\"><g transform=\"translate(0,0) scale(1,1)\"><path d=\"M0 96C0 60.7 28.7 32 64 32H448c35.3 0 64 28.7 64 64V416c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64H64c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64V96zM323.8 202.5c-4.5-6.6-11.9-10.5-19.8-10.5s-15.4 3.9-19.8 10.5l-87 127.6L170.7 297c-4.6-5.7-11.5-9-18.7-9s-14.2 3.3-18.7 9l-64 80c-5.8 7.2-6.9 17.1-2.9 25.4s12.4 13.6 21.6 13.6h96 32H424c8.9 0 17.1-4.9 21.2-12.8s3.6-17.4-1.4-24.7l-120-176zM112 192a48 48 0 1 0 0-96 48 48 0 1 0 0 96z\" fill=\"currentColor\" transform=\"translate(-256 -256)\"></path></g></g></svg></span></span></p>\n</div>\n\n  \n\n<div class=\"overlay-container svelte-wtx5ir\"><div class=\"overlay-background svelte-wtx5ir\"></div>\n  <div class=\"cards-and-buttons svelte-wtx5ir\"><div class=\"icon-container svelte-wtx5ir\"><div class=\"icon svelte-wtx5ir\" style=\"background-image: url(/sdgatlas/assets/icons/arrow-left.svg)\"></div></div>\n\n    \n\n    <div class=\"icon-container svelte-wtx5ir\"><div class=\"icon svelte-wtx5ir\" style=\"background-image: url(/sdgatlas/assets/icons/arrow-right.svg)\"></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n\n    \n    \n<footer class=\"simplified-footer loop\"><div class=\"row full-row-footer-components\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"lp__footer_top\"></div>\n      \n      <div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\"><div class=\"lp__footer_bottom\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\"><div class=\"lp__listinline\"><ul><li class=\"disclaimer\"><a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/about/legal\">Legal</a></li>\n                    <li class=\"disclaimer\"><a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/about/legal/privacy-notice\">Privacy Notice</a></li>\n                    <li class=\"disclaimer\"><a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/who-we-are/site-accessibility\">Site Accessibility</a></li>\n                    <li class=\"disclaimer\"><a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/access-to-information\">Access to Information</a></li>\n                    <li class=\"disclaimer\"><a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/about/careers\">Jobs</a></li>\n                    <li class=\"disclaimer\"><a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/about/contacts\">Contact</a></li></ul></div></div>\n              \n              <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-5 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\"><div class=\"lp__footer_fraud\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/about/legal/scams\">SCAM ALERT</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"https://wbgcmsprod.microsoftcrmportals.com/en-US/anonymous-users/int-fraud-management/create-new-complaint/\">REPORT FRAUD OR CORRUPTION</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div>\n          </div></div>\n      </div></div>\n  \n  \n  <div class=\"row full-row-footer-black-components\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"lp__footer_bottom_left\"><div class=\"col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.worldbank.org\"><img src=\"https://datatopics.worldbank.org/sdgatlas/assets/external/loop-header-footer/img/logo-wbg-footer-en.svg\" class=\"footer-logo\" title=\"World Bank Group logo\" alt=\"World Bank Group logo\"></a></li>\n              <li><a class=\"lp__wbgpartnership\" title=\"International Bank for Reconstruction and Development\" href=\"https://www.worldbank.org/en/who-we-are/ibrd\">IBRD</a></li>\n              <li><a class=\"lp__wbgpartnership\" title=\"International Development Association\" href=\"https://ida.worldbank.org/\">IDA</a></li>\n              <li><a class=\"lp__wbgpartnership\" title=\"International Finance Corporation\" href=\"https://www.ifc.org\">IFC</a></li>\n              <li><a class=\"lp__wbgpartnership\" title=\"Multilateral Investment Guarantee Agency\" href=\"https://www.miga.org/\">MIGA</a></li>\n              <li><a class=\"lp__wbgpartnership\" title=\"International Centre for Settlement of Investment Disputes\" href=\"https://icsid.worldbank.org\">ICSID</a></li></ul></div></div>\n        \n\n        <div class=\"lp__copyright\"><div class=\"col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">&copy; <span id=\"footer-year\"></span>\n            <script language=\"JavaScript\">var time = new Date();\n              var year = time.getYear();\n              if (year < 2000) year = year + 1900;\n              document.getElementById(\'footer-year\').innerHTML = year;\n              // End -->\n            </script>\n            The World Bank Group, All Rights Reserved.</div></div>\n        </div></div></div></footer>\n</div>\n</div></main>\n</div>\n\n\n			\n			<script>\n				{\n					__sveltekit_fx4enp = {\n						env: {},\n						assets: \"/sdgatlas\",\n						base: \"/sdgatlas\",\n						element: document.currentScript.parentElement\n					};\n\n					const data = [null,null,null];\n\n					Promise.all([\n						import(\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/entry/start.1c02d60e.js\"),\n						import(\"/sdgatlas/_app/immutable/entry/app.6ac145db.js\")\n					]).then(([kit, app]) => {\n						kit.start(app, __sveltekit_fx4enp.element, {\n							node_ids: [0, 2, 4],\n							data,\n							form: null,\n							error: null\n						});\n					});\n				}\n			</script>\n		</div>\n  </body>\n</html>\n', '2025-05-28 15:06:31', '重點1：文章標題與主題  \r\n  文章標題為「Life on land | SDG 15: Life on land」，聚焦於聯合國永續發展目標（SDG）第15項「陸地生命」，探討森林保護、生物多樣性及土地退化等議題。  \r\n\r\n重點2：森林的重要性  \r\n  - 森林覆蓋全球近三分之一的陸地面積，是80%以上陸地物種的棲息地。  \r\n  - 提供生態系統服務，如水源涵養（供應全球75%淡水）和碳匯功能（每年吸收約160億噸二氧化碳）。  \r\n  - 支持生計：約3-3.5億人依賴森林維生，超過10億人依靠森林產品獲取收入。  \r\n\r\n重點3：森林類型與分布  \r\n  - 分為四大類：熱帶、亞熱帶、溫帶和寒帶森林。  \r\n  - 熱帶森林生物多樣性最高，碳儲存能力是其他森林的兩倍。  \r\n  - 全球森林分布不均，俄羅斯、巴西、加拿大和中國佔全球森林面積的四分之一以上。  \r\n\r\n重點4：森林減少與退化  \r\n  - 2000-2020年間，全球森林面積減少2.4%（約1億公頃，相當於埃及國土面積）。  \r\n  - 主要原因包括：  \r\n    - 農業擴張（如大豆、棕櫚油生產）。  \r\n    - 城市化。  \r\n    - 火災（氣候變化加劇火災頻率）。  \r\n  - 熱帶地區損失最嚴重，如巴拉圭森林減少30%，而越南因政策保護增加23%。  \r\n\r\n重點5：樹木覆蓋損失的驅動因素  \r\n  - 臨時性損失（佔75%以上）：林業活動、火災、輪耕農業。  \r\n  - 永久性損失：商品農業（如拉丁美洲59%、東南亞80%）、城市化。  \r\n  - 區域差異：非洲以輪耕為主（94%），俄羅斯以火災為主（75%）。  \r\n\r\n重點6：氣候變遷與碳匯  \r\n  - 森林碳匯功能因砍伐而削弱，2019年全球人為溫室氣體排放為480億噸CO2e，森林吸收量佔三分之一。  \r\n  - 熱帶雨林（如亞馬遜、剛果盆地）仍是碳匯，但東南亞因砍伐已成為碳排放源。  \r\n\r\n重點7：生物多樣性威脅  \r\n  - 28%的評估物種（IUCN紅色名錄）面臨滅絕風險，主因是棲息地破壞。  \r\n  - 紅色名錄指數（RLI）顯示生物多樣性持續下降，尤其熱帶地區。  \r\n\r\n重點8：保護措施與國際框架  \r\n  - 關鍵生物多樣性區域（KBAs）的保護面積2000-2021年翻倍，但近年增速放緩。  \r\n  - 2022年《昆明-蒙特婁全球生物多樣性框架》提出2030年目標，包括保護30%陸地和海洋。  \r\n\r\n重點9：補充資料  \r\n  - SDG 15其他目標進展：  \r\n    - 目標15.9：部分國家未將生物多樣性納入發展策略。  \r\n    - 目標15.a：生物多樣性相關官方發展援助（ODA）金額波動。  \r\n\r\n資料來源：  \r\n- 聯合國糧農組織（FAO）、世界銀行、世界資源研究所（WRI）、國際自然保護聯盟（IUCN）等機構數據。');
INSERT INTO `article` (`ArticleID`, `Title`, `Category`, `ImageURL`, `Description`, `ArticleURL`, `UserID`, `Content`, `created_at`, `teacher_summary`) VALUES
(8, 'Seeing the Forest for the Trees', 'sdg15', 'uploads/6837277227abd_forest2.jpg', '探討永續發展目標 15 與其他永續發展目標之間的協同作用，強調土地管理的綜合方法。', 'https://www.un.org/en/chronicle/article/goal-15-seeing-forest-trees-making-most-synergies-achieve-sdgs-constrained-environment', 2, '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\"><head profile=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml/vocab\">\r\n		<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n		<meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge,chrome=1\">\r\n		<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n\r\n		<!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->\r\n		<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Tackling deforestation, land degradation, desertification and the protection of biodiversity cannot be treated in isolation: healthy ecosystems are the bedrock of poverty reduction efforts, resilient and productive farming, and water systems that underpin development and growth.\">\r\n		<meta name=\"author\" content=\"United Nations\">\r\n\r\n		<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Drupal 7 (http://drupal.org)\">\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/en/chronicle/article/goal-15-seeing-forest-trees-making-most-synergies-achieve-sdgs-constrained-environment\">\n<link rel=\"shortlink\" href=\"/en/node/25871\">\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://www.un.org/sites/un2.un.org/themes/bootstrap_un2/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/vnd.microsoft.icon\">\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag(\'js\', new Date());\n  gtag(\'config\', \'G-FFWXW7DVFF\');\n\n</script>\n\r\n		<title>Goal 15—Seeing the Forest for the Trees—Making the Most of Synergies to Achieve SDGs in a Constrained Environment  | United Nations</title>	\r\n\r\n                <meta name=\"DC.Title\" content=\"Goal 15—Seeing the Forest for the Trees—Making the Most of Synergies 