},\"title\":[{\"type\":\"heading3\",\"text\":\"By 2025, 1.8 Billion People Will be Living in Countries or Regions With Absolute Water Scarcity\",\"spans\":[]}],\"description\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"If you care about Goal 15 Life on Land, share this image and help make the #globalgoals famous\",\"spans\":[]}],\"slug\":\"absolute-water-scarcity\"},{\"image\":{},\"link\":{\"link_type\":\"Media\"},\"title\":[{\"type\":\"heading3\",\"text\":\"Jacqueline Fernandez supports Goal 15 &acirc;&#128;&#147; Life on Land\",\"spans\":[]}],\"description\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Jacqueline Fernandez supports Goal 15 Life on Land #globalgoals\",\"spans\":[]}],\"slug\":\"jacqueline-fernandez-supports-goal-15-life-on-land\"},{\"image\":{},\"link\":{\"link_type\":\"Media\"},\"title\":[{\"type\":\"heading3\",\"text\":\"The World\'s Forests are a Shared Stolen Treasure That We Must Put Back For Our Children\'s Future &acirc;&#128;&#147; Desmond Tutu\",\"spans\":[]}],\"description\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"I support Goal 15 - Life On Land #globalgoals\",\"spans\":[]}],\"slug\":\"life-on-land-archbishop-desmond-tutu-quote\"}],\"tips\":[{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Find a Goal 15 charity you want to support. Any donation, big or small, can make a difference! See the \\\"Get Involved\\\" section above.\",\"spans\":[]}]},{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Reduce your use of paper. Avoid printing and substitute it with electronic devices or carriers.\",\"spans\":[]}]},{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Don&acirc;&#128;&#153;t shop for pets! Visit your local animal shelter and adopt an animal there.\",\"spans\":[]}]},{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Don&acirc;&#128;&#153;t buy products tested on animals: Check the labels on the products you buy.\",\"spans\":[]}]},{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Recycle paper, glass, plastic, metal and old electronics.\",\"spans\":[]}]},{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Compost. Composting food scraps can reduce climate impact while also recycling nutrients.\",\"spans\":[]}]},{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Clean your local parks and forests. Organise your own or join an existing clean-up event to sustain the ecosystem of your local green space.\",\"spans\":[]}]},{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Don\'t use pesticides. To protect and sustain the quality of soil, don&acirc;&#128;&#153;t use chemicals while growing plants.\",\"spans\":[]}]},{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Volunteer with street animal organizations or shelters: Help to sustain diversity and save lives of animal species by volunteering in organizations helping these pets as well as endangered species.\",\"spans\":[]}]},{\"text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"Stay informed. Follow your local news and stay in touch with the Global Goals online or on social media at&Acirc;&nbsp;@TheGlobalGoals.\",\"spans\":[{\"start\":107,\"end\":122,\"type\":\"hyperlink\",\"data\":{\"link_type\":\"Web\",\"url\":\"https://twitter.com/TheGlobalGoals\",\"target\":\"_blank\"}}]}]}],\"number\":15,\"icon_text\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"&eacute;&#153;&cedil;&aring;&#159;&#159;&ccedil;&#148;&#159;&aelig;&#133;&#139;\",\"spans\":[]},{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"text\":\"\",\"spans\":[]}],\"slug\":\"life-on-land\",\"legacy_slug\":\"life-on-land\"}}],\"error\":null,\"isLoading\":false},\"articles\":{\"items\":[],\"pages\":[],\"tags\":[\"goal-15\"],\"pageSize\":8,\"page\":1,\"error\":null,\"isLoading\":false,\"total\":null},\"events\":{\"DOMCONTENTLOADED\":\"DOMContentLoaded\",\"DOMTITLECHANGE\":\"DOMTitleChange\",\"REPLACESTATE\":\"replaceState\",\"PUSHSTATE\":\"pushState\",\"NAVIGATE\":\"navigate\",\"POPSTATE\":\"popState\",\"RENDER\":\"render\"},\"components\":{},\"cache\":null,\"href\":\"/15-life-on-land\",\"route\":\":path\",\"title\":\"&ccedil;&#155;&reg;&aelig;&uml;&#153; 15: &eacute;&#153;&cedil;&aring;&#159;&#159;&ccedil;&#148;&#159;&aelig;&#133;&#139; | &aring;&#133;&uml;&ccedil;&#144;&#131;&ccedil;&#155;&reg;&aelig;&uml;&#153;\"}</script></body></html>\n', '2025-05-28 15:24:03', '重點1：目標15 - 保護和恢復陸地生態系統\r\n    陸地上的繁榮生命是我們在地球上生活的基礎。我們都是地球生態系統的一部分，但通過森林砍伐、自然棲息地喪失和土地退化，我們對其造成了嚴重破壞。促進生態系統的可持續利用和保護生物多樣性不僅是一項事業，更是我們自身生存的關鍵。\r\n\r\n重點2：目標15的12個具體目標\r\n    1. 目標15.1：保護和恢復陸地生態系統\r\n        - 到2020年，確保陸地生態系統的保護、恢復和可持續利用。\r\n    2. 目標15.2：促進森林的可持續管理\r\n        - 到2020年，實施森林的可持續管理，防止森林退化。\r\n    3. 目標15.3：防治荒漠化和恢復退化土地\r\n        - 到2020年，防治荒漠化，恢復退化的土地和土壤。\r\n    4. 目標15.4：保護山地生態系統\r\n        - 到2030年，保護山地生態系統及其生物多樣性。\r\n    5. 目標15.5：保護生物多樣性\r\n        - 採取緊急行動減少自然棲息地的破壞，保護受威脅物種。\r\n    6. 目標15.6：促進遺傳資源的公平分享\r\n        - 確保遺傳資源的公平和公正分享。\r\n    7. 目標15.7：打擊非法野生動植物貿易\r\n        - 採取行動打擊非法野生動植物貿易。\r\n    8. 目標15.8：防止外來物種入侵\r\n        - 到2020年，防止外來物種入侵及其對生態系統的影響。\r\n    9. 目標15.9：將生態系統和生物多樣性納入國家規劃\r\n        - 將生態系統和生物多樣性價值納入國家和地方規劃。\r\n    10. 目標15.a：增加對生物多樣性的資金支持\r\n        - 增加對生物多樣性和生態系統的資金支持。\r\n    11. 目標15.b：動員資源保護森林\r\n        - 動員資源保護和可持續管理森林。\r\n    12. 目標15.c：支持打擊偷獵和非法貿易\r\n        - 加強全球支持打擊偷獵和非法野生動植物貿易。\r\n\r\n重點3：如何參與\r\n    1. 支持目標15的慈善機構：任何捐款都能產生影響。\r\n    2. 減少紙張使用：避免打印，改用電子設備。\r\n    3. 領養寵物：從當地動物收容所領養，而非購買。\r\n    4. 避免購買動物測試產品：檢查產品標籤。\r\n    5. 回收：回收紙張、玻璃、塑料、金屬和電子產品。\r\n    6. 堆肥：減少氣候影響並回收營養物質。\r\n    7. 清潔當地公園和森林：參與或組織清潔活動。\r\n    8. 避免使用農藥：保護土壤質量。\r\n    9. 志願服務：參與動物保護組織的志願活動。\r\n    10. 保持關注：通過社交媒體關注全球目標的最新動態。\r\n\r\n重點4：相關資源與合作夥伴\r\n    1. 項目合作夥伴：Project Everyone、The New Division by Trollbäck + Company、code and conspire。\r\n    2. 社交媒體平台：Facebook、Twitter、Instagram、YouTube。\r\n    3. 內容信息：條款、隱私政策、反貪腐政策、資產許可等。\r\n\r\n重點5：總結\r\n    保護陸地生態系統是全球可持續發展的重要目標，需要個人、組織和政府的共同努力。通過具體行動和參與，我們可以共同實現這一目標，確保地球生態系統的健康和生物多樣性的保護。');
