(22, 'Taking Urgent Action to Combat Climate Change', 'sdg13', 'uploads/68373e03730a7_ef8ad03c7ffcd693.png', '這篇文章分析了實現SDG 15的進展與持續挑戰，特別聚焦於非洲地區，並探討數據在監測保護陸地生態系統中的重要角色。', 'https://www.un.org/en/chronicle/article/goal-13-taking-urgent-action-combat-climate-change-sdgs-and-paris-climate-agreement', 5, '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\"><head profile=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml/vocab\">\r\n		<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n		<meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge,chrome=1\">\r\n		<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n\r\n		<!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->\r\n		<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Today more people are employed in the renewable energy industry globally than in the oil and gas sectors. In fact, worldwide, an estimated 5.7 million people were employed directly or indirectly in the global renewable energy industry in 2012—a figure that could triple by 2030. Investing in forests or smart agriculture, including organic farming, can also improve environmental sustainability, combat climate change, generate jobs and deliver further support for the SDGs.\">\r\n		<meta name=\"author\" content=\"United Nations\">\r\n\r\n		<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Drupal 7 (http://drupal.org)\">\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/en/chronicle/article/goal-13-taking-urgent-action-combat-climate-change-sdgs-and-paris-climate-agreement\">\n<link rel=\"shortlink\" href=\"/en/node/25865\">\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://www.un.org/sites/un2.un.org/themes/bootstrap_un2/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/vnd.microsoft.icon\">\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag(\'js\', new Date());\n  gtag(\'config\', \'G-FFWXW7DVFF\');\n\n</script>\n\r\n		<title>Goal 13—Taking Urgent Action to Combat