tional Monetary Fund</a><ul class=\"sub-menu\"><li id=\"menu-item-137288\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-137288\"><a href=\"https://www.openigo.com/imf-internship-program-2020-products-services/\">IMF Fund Internship: Products &amp; Services</a></li><li id=\"menu-item-137287\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-137287\"><a href=\"https://www.openigo.com/organizations/imf-internship/\">IMF Fund Internship: Overview</a></li><li id=\"menu-item-137284\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-137284\"><a href=\"https://openigo.com/imf-jobs-and-careers-products-services/\">IMF Jobs and Careers: Products &amp; Services</a></li><li id=\"menu-item-137289\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-137289\"><a href=\"https://www.openigo.com/organizations/imf-jobs-overview/\">IMF Jobs and Careers: Overview</a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li id=\"menu-item-10133\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-10133\"><a href=\"https://openigo.com/about-us/meet-our-coaches/\">Coaching</a></li><li id=\"menu-item-222892\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-222892\"><a href=\"https://openigo.com/training-workshops/\">Workshops</a></li><li id=\"menu-item-398\" class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-398\"><a href=\"https://openigo.com/online-magazine/\">Magazine</a></li><li id=\"menu-item-18229\" class=\"visible-xs btn btn--sm btn--primary type--uppercase menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-18229\"><a href=\"https://www.openigo.com/shop/\">Store</a></li><li><div class=\"hidden-xs btn btn--sm btn--primary type--uppercase\">\n<a class=\"btn__text\" href=\"/shop\" title=\"Store\">Store</a></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></nav></div><div id=\"start\"></div><div class=\"main-container\"><section class=\"imagebg space--sm overflow-hidden\" data-overlay=\"4\"><div class=\"background-image-holder filter-blur\">\n<img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://openigo.com/data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxOTIwIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjIyMCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDE5MjAgMjIwIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBzdHlsZT0iZmlsbDojY2ZkNGRiO2ZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eTogMC4xOyIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" width=\"1920\" height=\"220\" data-src=\"https://openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/shutterstock_116821555-1920x220.jpg\" alt=\"Understanding the SDGs: Goal 13 and the importance of climate action\"></div><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-sm-12\"><h1>Online Magazine</h1></div></div></div></section><section id=\"post-content\" class=\"bg--white space--xs\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-sm-10 col-md-8 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-offset-2\"><article><div class=\"article__title text-center\"><h1 class=\"h2\">Understanding the SDGs: Goal 13 and the importance of climate action</h1>\n<span>September 14, 2021</span></div><div class=\"article__body content-post\"><p class=\"yoast-reading-time__wrapper\"><span class=\"yoast-reading-time__icon\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-icon=\"clock\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:-0.1em\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"yoast-reading-time__spacer\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:1em\"></span><span class=\"yoast-reading-time__descriptive-text\">Estimated reading time:  </span><span class=\"yoast-reading-time__reading-time\">4</span><span class=\"yoast-reading-time__time-unit\"> minutes</span></p><div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://www.openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/climate-action-4150536_1280.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://openigo.com/data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDI0IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjY4MiIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjQgNjgyIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBzdHlsZT0iZmlsbDojY2ZkNGRiO2ZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eTogMC4xOyIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" data-src=\"https://www.openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/climate-action-4150536_1280-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"sdg climate action\" class=\"wp-image-170443\" data-srcset=\"https://openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/climate-action-4150536_1280-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/climate-action-4150536_1280-300x200.jpg 300w, https://openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/climate-action-4150536_1280-768x512.jpg 768w, https://openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/climate-action-4150536_1280.jpg 1280w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"></a></figure></div><p>The <a href=\"https://openigo.com/category/international-development\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs)</a> are goals created by the United Nations in 2015 in order to provide a detailed framework for public, private, and civil society actors globally to bring about significant and transformative change towards a world that works for 100% of humanity and the planet as a whole.</p><p>In this article, we will show you what is the thirteenth of these goals (the SDG about climate action) and its importance!</p><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8a7f81c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading animated slideInDown\" data-id=\"8a7f81c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\'{\"_animation\":\"slideInDown\"}\' data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-medium\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Do you want to have a successful career in International Development?</strong></p><p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-medium\">Are you tired of facing <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>long selection processes</strong></span> only to end up with <strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">fruitless results</span></strong>? Are application documents and interviews <strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">too difficult</span></strong>? Do you have to face a highly qualified competition that constantly gets the vacancies you apply for?</p><p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-medium\">There&rsquo;s a ladder to get to your dream job and we are here to help you climb it!</p><p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-medium\">Look no further: with our <strong>complete eBook,</strong> you will change the way you apply for a selection process and you will highly improve your perfomance, finally <strong>achieving the job of your dreams</strong> in a meaningful International Development career!</p><p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-medium\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Don&rsquo;t miss this opportunity:</strong></p></div></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a class=\"fasc-button fasc-size-large fasc-type-glossy fasc-rounded-medium fasc-ico-before dashicons-admin-site fasc-style-bold\" style=\"background-color: #009ddb; color: #ffffff;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www.openigo.com/kick-starting-your-career-in-international-development/\">KICK-START YOUR INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT CAREER NOW!</a></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Are you a UN YPP applicant? Do you want to understand all the aspects of the UN YPP Written Examination Stage? <a href=\"https://www.openigo.com/un-ypp-written-exam-stage-understanding-the-examination/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Then check out our article on the topic!</a></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\" id=\"block-3d3231dd-ae99-487d-9d1c-9d8d94103961\"><strong>What is Goal 13 of the SDGs?</strong></h3><p>The thirteenth goal of the SDGs is aimed at adopting urgent measures to stop climate change, which is affecting every nation of the world. This SDG involves a sophisticated understanding of climate change and related issues as a set of topics that relate to the environment as well as economics and human rights.</p><p></p><h3 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-what-is-the-importance-of-the-climate-action-sdg\"><strong>What is the importance of the climate action SDG?</strong></h3><p>Greenhouse gas (GG) levels in the atmosphere have been rising gradually since the Industrial Revolution; the sea level rose by 19 centimeters between 1901 and 2010; the Arctic is losing 1.07 million km2 of ice every decade.</p><p>All this suggests that the Earth&rsquo;s weather patterns are changing and human activity is the main responsible for that. Climate change has a very negative impact on the environment, the economy, human societies and communities and, if fast action is not taken, the consequences will be devastating for life and for the development of the planet.</p><p></p><p></p><h3 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-what-types-of-policies-are-in-line-with-goal-10\"><strong>What types of policies are in line with Goal 10?</strong></h3><p>The types of policies that are in line with the climate action SDG are:</p><ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Policies aimed at strengthening resilience and adaptive capacity to climate-related hazards and natural disasters in all countries;</li><li>Policies aimed at integrating climate change measures into national policies, strategies and planning;</li><li>Policies aimed at improving education, awareness-raising and human and institutional capacity on climate change mitigation, adaptation, impact reduction and early warning;</li><li>Policies aimed at implementing the commitment undertaken by developed-country parties to the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change.</li></ul><p></p><h3 class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-all-the-sdgs-in-one-glimpse\"><strong>All the <a href=\"https://sdgs.un.org/goals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SDGs</a> in one glimpse</strong></h3><div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https://www.openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/%E0%A6%9F%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%95%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%87_%E0%A6%89%E0%A6%A8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC%E0%A6%A8_%E0%A6%B2%E0%A6%95%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B7%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%AE%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A4%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://openigo.com/data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI3NjgiIGhlaWdodD0iNTkzIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNzY4IDU5MyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-src=\"https://www.openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/&#2463;&#2503;&#2453;&#2488;&#2439;_&#2441;&#2472;&#2509;&#2472;&#2479;&#2492;&#2472;_&#2482;&#2453;&#2509;&#2487;&#2509;&#2479;&#2478;&#2494;&#2468;&#2509;&#2480;&#2494;-1024x791.png\" alt=\"sdg climate action\" class=\"wp-image-159503\" width=\"768\" height=\"593\" data-srcset=\"https://openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/&#2463;&#2503;&#2453;&#2488;&#2439;_&#2441;&#2472;&#2509;&#2472;&#2479;&#2492;&#2472;_&#2482;&#2453;&#2509;&#2487;&#2509;&#2479;&#2478;&#2494;&#2468;&#2509;&#2480;&#2494;-1024x791.png 1024w, https://openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/&#2463;&#2503;&#2453;&#2488;&#2439;_&#2441;&#2472;&#2509;&#2472;&#2479;&#2492;&#2472;_&#2482;&#2453;&#2509;&#2487;&#2509;&#2479;&#2478;&#2494;&#2468;&#2509;&#2480;&#2494;-300x232.png 300w, https://openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/&#2463;&#2503;&#2453;&#2488;&#2439;_&#2441;&#2472;&#2509;&#2472;&#2479;&#2492;&#2472;_&#2482;&#2453;&#2509;&#2487;&#2509;&#2479;&#2478;&#2494;&#2468;&#2509;&#2480;&#2494;-768x593.png 768w, https://openigo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/&#2463;&#2503;&#2453;&#2488;&#2439;_&#2441;&#2472;&#2509;&#2472;&#2479;&#2492;&#2472;_&#2482;&#2453;&#2509;&#2487;&#2509;&#2479;&#2478;&#2494;&#2468;&#2509;&#2480;&#2494;.png 1650w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"></a></figure></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Would like to know more about UN internship opportunities? Then check our UN Internships overview:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a class=\"fasc-button fasc-size-large fasc-type-glossy fasc-rounded-medium fasc-ico-before dashicons-awards fasc-style-bold\" style=\"background-color: #009ddb; color: #ffffff;\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.openigo.com/un-internships-overview/\" rel=\"noopener\">UN Internships Overview</a></span></p><p></p><p><strong>Do you have an interest in an international career at the UN?</strong> In pursuit of its mission, the OpenIGO network has prepared a <strong>comprehensive eBook</strong> and <strong>support and guidance services</strong> with the aim of highly increasing your chances of success in the UN YPP selection process!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.openigo.com/un-ypp/products-services/#un-ypp-exam-preparation-book-manual-for-candidates\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Our comprehensive <strong>eBook </strong></a>will help you perform successfully in the United Nations YPP selection process. It will introduce you to the complex world of the United Nations and it will guide you through all the stages of this competitive selection process. This eBook was written and revised by a team of professors, human resources specialists, and former young professionals with a great deal of diligence.</p><p>In addition, we have developed&nbsp;<strong>support and guidance services</strong>. These services include revising your UN YPP application documents (essay, curriculum vitae, and thesis/dissertation short summaries) and a <strong>mock interview</strong> as per the United Nations YPP model.</p><p>Having a mock interview with a professional who has extensive experience and knowledge of the UN YPP interview model will help you be better prepared for this phase, greatly increasing your chances of being selected for the desired vacancy.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>WOULD YOU LIKE TO KNOW MORE ABOUT OUR UN YPP PRODUCTS &amp; SERVICES?</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a class=\"fasc-button fasc-size-large fasc-type-glossy fasc-rounded-medium fasc-ico-before dashicons-awards fasc-style-bold\" style=\"background-color: #009ddb; color: #ffffff;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www.openigo.com/un-ypp/products-services/\">UN YPP &ndash; Products and Services</a></span></p><p></p>							<br clear=\"all\"></div></article></div></div></div></section><section class=\"space--xxs\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row article__share text-center no-margin\"><div class=\"col-md-4 col-xs-6\">\n<a class=\"btn bg--facebook btn--icon\" href=\"//www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://openigo.com/understanding-the-sdgs-goal-13-and-the-importance-of-climate-action/\">\n<span class=\"btn__text\">\n<i class=\"socicon socicon-facebook\"></i>\nShare on Facebook\n</span>\n</a></div><div class=\"col-md-4 col-xs-6 mb--1\">\n<a class=\"btn bg--twitter btn--icon\" href=\"//twitter.com/share?url=https://openigo.com/understanding-the-sdgs-goal-13-and-the-importance-of-climate-action/&amp;text=Understanding%20the%20SDGs:%20Goal%2013%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20climate%20action\">\n<span class=\"btn__text\">\n<i class=\"socico