ed up and applied more widely and equitably, they can support deep emissions reductions.</p>\n    </blockquote>\n    <svg width=\"34px\" height=\"26px\" viewbox=\"0 0 34 26\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\">\n      <title>bxs-quote-alt-right</title>\n      <g stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\">\n        <g transform=\"translate(-255.000000, -228.000000)\" fill=\"var(--contrast)\" fill-rule=\"nonzero\">\n          <g transform=\"translate(255.000000, 229.000000)\">\n            <path d=\"M32.9109454,5.94024755 L32.8698186,5.65971377 L32.8270467,5.66973283 C32.0141848,1.81121052 28.3996786,-0.751912636 24.5507896,-0.199137053 C20.7019005,0.353638531 17.9297973,3.83400343 18.203411,7.76997231 C18.4770247,11.7059412 21.7031456,14.7566805 25.5903693,14.7553535 C25.9572206,14.7553535 26.3092663,14.6985788 26.6596669,14.6468137 C26.5461569,15.0342174 26.4293567,15.4283006 26.2418183,15.7823075 C26.0542799,16.2966194 25.7614569,16.7424678 25.4702789,17.1916558 C25.2268081,17.6775803 24.797444,18.0065396 24.4815899,18.4223307 C24.1509301,18.826433 23.7001801,19.0952778 23.3431992,19.4309164 C22.9927986,19.7815837 22.5338231,19.9569173 22.1686168,20.2040542 C21.7869598,20.4261434 21.454655,20.6716105 21.0993192,20.7884995 L20.2126247,21.1592049 L19.4328599,21.4881641 L20.2290754,24.7259915 L21.2111842,24.4855339 C21.5253932,24.4053814 21.9086953,24.3118702 22.3446397,24.1999906 C22.7904545,24.1164984 23.2658807,23.8877298 23.7955943,23.6789993 C24.3170826,23.4402117 24.9241146,23.2815765 25.4867297,22.8991822 C26.0526349,22.5351563 26.705729,22.2312447 27.2815046,21.7436503 C27.8391845,21.2410272 28.5120194,20.805198 29.0088316,20.1673176 C29.5517058,19.5695135 30.0879997,18.9416522 30.5042032,18.226959 C30.9862097,17.5456627 31.3135793,16.7975726 31.6590447,16.0578318 C31.9716086,15.3180909 32.2233048,14.5616516 32.428939,13.8269203 C32.8188213,12.354118 32.9931991,10.954788