ure>\n\n    \n  \n	\n\n\n  \n  \n    <div class=\"general-text\">\n	<p><strong>Role of investors</strong></p>\n<p><em>&ldquo;Investors have a leading role to play in this process,&rdquo; said Shelagh Whitley, chief sustainability officer at the Principles for Responsible Investment, a UN-supported network of investors.</em></p>\n<p><em>&ldquo;The IPCC report notes that investors are raising awareness of climate change as a financial risk. However, climate-related financial risks, whether from physical climate impacts or from a disorderly transition to a low-carbon economy, are still greatly underestimated by parts of the industry.&rdquo;</em></p>\n<p><em>Sylvian Vanston, head of climate change investment research at analyst MSCI, echoed the sentiment, saying policymakers need to do more to encourage this.</em></p>\n<p>&ldquo;This includes advocating for policies that provide a clear incentive framework for net zero,&rdquo; said Vanston. &ldquo;This is not about more regulation but about better regulation to level the playing field. We all know we need more low-carbon energy, but we also need policymakers who heed climate science.&rdquo;<em><br></em></p>\n</div>\n    \n  \n	\n\n\n  \n</div>\n\n        \n        \n        <div class=\"uppercase font-avenir-bold text-14px\">\n          <span class=\"font-avenir-black\">Content Tags:</span>\n          <a class=\"underline text-primary-dark hover:text-primary\" href=\"https://www.netzeroinvestor.net/category/esg\">ESG</a>&nbsp; \n        \n        \n          <a class=\"underline text-primary-dark hover:text-primary\" href=\"https://www.netzeroinvestor.net/category/emissions\">Emissions</a>&nbsp; \n        </div>\n\n        \n        \n        <div class=\"social-media-share\" x-cloak x-data=\"socialWidget\">\n\n    <button class=\"social-media-share__share-button\" title=\"Share content\">\n        <div class=\"social-media-share__share-button-inner\">\n            <span class=\"social-media-share__share-button-text\">S